body_html:
This is part of tensorflow's bazel packages. So this is supposed to be run like this:

cd tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/factorization
bazel test :gmm_ops_test :gmm_test

or just do:

bazel test tensorflow/contrib/factorization:all

for all packages related to factorization (i.e. kmeans and gmm so far).

body:
This is part of tensorflow's [bazel](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources) packages. So this is supposed to be run like this:

    cd tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/factorization
    bazel test :gmm_ops_test :gmm_test

or just do:

    bazel test tensorflow/contrib/factorization:all

for all packages related to factorization (i.e. kmeans and gmm so far).
